snippet.title: Webinar with DIT: improve eBay store performance with Item Specifics and prepare for eBay's mandates
snippet.description:
Recording of the webinar we co-hosted with the Department for International Trade on 11 February 2021. Through this webinar, our Customer Sucess Specialist Chris Cook discusses what Item Specifics are and why they are important, and how to prepare for the eBay Item Specifics mandate for 22nd February 2021. The video includes a demonstration of some of the Optiseller tools and Aspect Finder+ and a final Q&A.

Sign up for your free 7 day trial at www.optiseller.com/pricing
